Steps.Message: Update at 12:09 - We've remotely diverted electricity around the faulty part of the network, restoring power to 463 additional properties. This leaves 533 properties affected by the underground network fault. We'll keep sending text updates to everyone until all the power to your area is on. To stop receiving texts, just follow this link https://bit.ly/348KOZ3 to unsubscribe, or send CANCEL to 80876 (standard text fees apply).

We became aware of this power cut at 09:45. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
